[b]Expeditions[/b][s]
From [Town] You can spend gold to explore while away via Expeditions. The rate is 1 gold per hour, per zone you choose to explore in, and you can send multiple expeditions at a time (only 1 per zone though). You can purchase the Star Map [supply] perk to significantly increase expedition effectiveness.[/s]
